biostar_privacy_notice_agreement_descrip: This Privacy Notice applies to administrators and authorized users of the BioStar Air service (“Service”) provided by Suprema Inc.

As a Site Administrator, you may register usernames, departments, mobile credentials, and biometric templates (face or fingerprint) on behalf of your organization. Suprema does not use this information for any purpose beyond service delivery and support, as described in the Privacy Policy and Data Processing Agreement.

You are responsible for managing your users’ personal information in accordance with your organization’s policies and applicable law. Suprema is not responsible for personal data handling practices outside its control.
This Privacy Notice may be updated periodically. In the event of material changes, Suprema will notify registered administrators in advance using the contact information on file.
By selecting “I agree,” you confirm that you have read and understood this Privacy Notice as a Site Administrator for BioStar Air.
